Getting Support on Our Discord Server



You're welcome to request support on our Discord server. We've set up a special section just for CCD students. To enter this section, just link your Discord account to your CyberDefenders account.

Before reaching out with an issue or request for assistance, please review the earlier message history and check the course FAQ.

  1. Post any course-related questions in the #ccd-private channel.
  2. Post lab-related questions under the #ccd-labs category. Each lab has a dedicated channel (e.g., #Suricata, #Rita, #Nessus..etc). 
  3. Have an account-related problem (e.g., enrollment problems)? , Send a direct message to @Premium_Support user with details about the problem you face (i.e., screenshots and links).
